OL,6,FThe Steel Industry (Special Measures)
OL,7,FBill would give the business secretary
OL,8,Fthe powers to prevent the Chinese
OL,9,Fowner of the plant, Jingye, from
OL,10,Fclosing blast furnaces at the site.
OL,12,FOn Friday, Prime Minister Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fsaid the country's economic and
OL,14,Fnational security are "on the line"
OL,15,Fand he planned to "take control" of
OL,16,Fthe steel plant, but stopped short of
OL,17,Ffull nationalisation.
