OL,6,FMPs will sit in the House of Commons
OL,7,Ffrom 11am and the House of Lords from
OL,8,F12pm in what will be the first
OL,9,Fparliamentary recall on a Saturday
OL,10,Fsince 1982, when MPs returned after
OL,11,Fthe Falklands War began.
OL,13,FThere have only been 34 recalls since
OL,14,F1948 with other significant recalls
OL,15,Fincluding a midweek sitting in August
OL,16,F2021 during the summer recess to
OL,17,Fdebate the evacuation from Afghanistan.
